HEADWORD: Tartronic
<hw>Tar*tron"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Tartro-</ets> + mal<ets>onic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or designating, an organic acid (called also
<xex>hydroxy malonic acid</xex>) obtained, by reducing mesoxalic acid,
as a white crystalline substance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

